%F A201455 G.f.: (2-3*x)/((1+x)*(1-4*x)).
%F A201455 a(n) = 4^n+(-1)^n.
%F A201455 a(n) = A086341(A047524(n)) for n>0, a(0)=2.
%F A201455 a(n) = [x^n] ( (1 + 3*x + sqrt(1 + 6*x + 25*x^2))/2 )^n for n >= 1. - _Peter Bala_, Jun 23 2015
